The paper discusses the feasibility of implementing Attribute-Based Encryption (ABE) on mobile devices, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The implementation also involves computational and energy consumption aspects, which are related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), cybernetics (cs.CY), and systems and control (cs.SY).
